trans-unit.source: Performs composition for containers.
trans-unit.target: Utför sammansättning för behållare.

trans-unit.source: This class is used internally by <xref:System.ComponentModel.Composition.Hosting.CompositionContainer>.
trans-unit.target: Den här klassen används internt av <xref:System.ComponentModel.Composition.Hosting.CompositionContainer>.</xref:System.ComponentModel.Composition.Hosting.CompositionContainer>

trans-unit.source: You should generally not use it unless you are authoring a container.
trans-unit.target: Du ska normalt inte använda det om du skapar en behållare.

trans-unit.source: > [!IMPORTANT] > This type implements the <xref:System.IDisposable> interface.
trans-unit.target: > [!IMPORTANT] > Den här typen implementerar den <xref:System.IDisposable>gränssnitt.</xref:System.IDisposable>

trans-unit.source: When you have finished using the type, you should dispose of it either directly or indirectly.
trans-unit.target: När du är klar med typ, ta bort den direkt eller indirekt.

trans-unit.source: To dispose of the type directly, call its <xref:System.IDisposable.Dispose%2A> method in a `try`/`catch` block.
trans-unit.target: Om du vill ta bort av typen direkt, anropa dess <xref:System.IDisposable.Dispose%2A>metod i en `try` / `catch` block.</xref:System.IDisposable.Dispose%2A>

trans-unit.source: To dispose of it indirectly, use a language construct such as `using` (in C#) or `Using` (in Visual Basic).
trans-unit.target: Om du vill ta hand om den indirekt, använda en språk-konstruktion som `using` (i C#) eller `Using` (i Visual Basic).

trans-unit.source: For more information, see the “Using an Object that Implements IDisposable” section in the <xref:System.IDisposable> interface topic.
trans-unit.target: Mer information finns i avsnittet "Med hjälp av ett objekt som implementerar IDisposable" i den <xref:System.IDisposable>gränssnittet avsnittet.</xref:System.IDisposable>

trans-unit.source: An object that specifies options that affect the behavior of the engine.
trans-unit.target: Ett objekt som anger alternativ som påverkar motorn.

trans-unit.source: Releases all resources used by the current instance of the <xref href="System.ComponentModel.Composition.Hosting.ImportEngine"></xref> class.
trans-unit.target: Frigör alla resurser som används av den aktuella instansen av den <xref href="System.ComponentModel.Composition.Hosting.ImportEngine"> </xref> klass.

trans-unit.source: Call `Dispose` when you are finished using the <xref:System.ComponentModel.Composition.Hosting.ImportEngine>.
trans-unit.target: Anropa `Dispose` när du är klar med hjälp av <xref:System.ComponentModel.Composition.Hosting.ImportEngine>.</xref:System.ComponentModel.Composition.Hosting.ImportEngine>

trans-unit.source: The `Dispose` method leaves the <xref:System.ComponentModel.Composition.Hosting.ImportEngine> in an unusable state.
trans-unit.target: Den `Dispose` metoden lämnar kvar det <xref:System.ComponentModel.Composition.Hosting.ImportEngine>oanvändbar.</xref:System.ComponentModel.Composition.Hosting.ImportEngine>

trans-unit.source: After calling `Dispose`, you must release all references to the <xref:System.ComponentModel.Composition.Hosting.ImportEngine> so the garbage collector can reclaim the memory that the <xref:System.ComponentModel.Composition.Hosting.ImportEngine> was occupying.
trans-unit.target: Efter att `Dispose`, måste du släppa alla referenser till den <xref:System.ComponentModel.Composition.Hosting.ImportEngine>så skräpinsamlingen kan frigöra minne som den <xref:System.ComponentModel.Composition.Hosting.ImportEngine>var upptar.</xref:System.ComponentModel.Composition.Hosting.ImportEngine> </xref:System.ComponentModel.Composition.Hosting.ImportEngine>

trans-unit.source: For more information, see [Cleaning Up Unmanaged Resources](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md) and [Implementing a Dispose Method](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md).
trans-unit.target: Mer information finns i [Rensa ohanterade resurser](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md) och [implementera en metod för ta bort](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md).

trans-unit.source: > [!NOTE] > Always call `Dispose` before you release your last reference to the <xref:System.ComponentModel.Composition.Hosting.ImportEngine>.
trans-unit.target: > [!NOTE] > Alltid anropet `Dispose` innan du släpper senaste referens till <xref:System.ComponentModel.Composition.Hosting.ImportEngine>.</xref:System.ComponentModel.Composition.Hosting.ImportEngine>

trans-unit.source: Otherwise, the resources it is using will not be freed until the garbage collector calls the <xref:System.ComponentModel.Composition.Hosting.ImportEngine> object's `Finalize` method.
trans-unit.target: De resurser som den använder frigörs annars inte förrän skräpinsamlingen anrop av <xref:System.ComponentModel.Composition.Hosting.ImportEngine>objektets `Finalize` metod.</xref:System.ComponentModel.Composition.Hosting.ImportEngine>

trans-unit.source: Releases the unmanaged resources used by the <xref href="System.ComponentModel.Composition.Hosting.ImportEngine"></xref> and optionally releases the managed resources.
trans-unit.target: Släpper de ohanterade resurser som används av den <xref href="System.ComponentModel.Composition.Hosting.ImportEngine"> </xref> och släpper du de hantera resurserna.

trans-unit.source: <xref uid="langword_csharp_true" name="true" href=""></xref> to release both managed and unmanaged resources; <xref uid="langword_csharp_false" name="false" href=""></xref> to release only unmanaged resources.
trans-unit.target: <xref uid="langword_csharp_true" name="true" href=""></xref>Frisläpp både hanterade och ohanterade resurser. <xref uid="langword_csharp_false" name="false" href=""> </xref> att släppa endast resurser som inte hanteras.
